(196, 1, '2013-06-27 15:53:31', '2013-06-27 15:53:31', 'OJT APPLICATION REQUIREMENTS\n<div>qAPPLICATION LETTER STATING:</div>\n<div>ØOBJECTIVE/S</div>\n<div>ØAREA/S OF INTEREST</div>\n<div>qSCHOOL RECOMMENDATION</div>\n<div>qRESUME</div>\n<div>q2 PCS. (2X2) RECENT ID PICTURE (WHITE BACKGROUND)</div>\n<div>q1 HALF BODY PICTURE (ATTIRE:UNIFORM/CORPORATE 3R SIZE)</div>\n<div>qWAIVER (DULY NOTARIZED)</div>\n<div>qNBI CLEARANCE (1 ORIGINAL COPY AND 2 PHOTOCOPIES)</div>\n<div>q</div>\n“NO ON-THE-JOB TRAINING FEE”\n\n&nbsp;\n\nPLEASE ADDRESS THE LETTER TO:\n\nMGEN JOSE ANGEL A. HONRADO AFP (RET)\n\nGENERAL MANAGER\n\nMANILA INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT AUTHORITY\n\nMIAA ADMIN BLDG. NAIA COMPLEX, PASAY CITY', 'OJT', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-autosave', '', '', '2013-06-27 15:53:31', '2013-06-27 15:53:31', '', 18, 'http://localhost/wordpress/18-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
